tafsir[3]{c,v,t}:
  14,45,"\"And ye dwelt in the dwellings of men who wronged their own souls; ye were clearly shown how We dealt with them; and We put forth (many) parables in your behoof!\""
  14,49,"And thou wilt see the sinners that day bound together in fetters;-"
  14,51,"That Allah may requite each soul according to its deserts; and verily Allah is swift in calling to account."